               <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard ">Incorrect Alarm Settings</typeofhazard>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">Do not change the alarm or warning thresholds unless the
