and configuration for each specific battery setup.</howtoavoid>
            </messagepanel>
         </hazardstatement>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To change the alarm threshold
values:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Navigate to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Devices &gt; BACS &gt; Alarm Thresholds</uicontrol> from the side menu.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Here it is possible to change the different alarm thresholds
and other settings for each type of alarm/warning:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Impedance</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Voltage</p>
                           <note class="- topic/note ">It is possible to set a delay for the voltage
alarm.</note>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Temperature</p>
                        </li>
                     </ul>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Apply</uicontrol> to confirm any changes.</p>
